<h1>New Post</h1>

<div class="row">
  <div class="span4">
    <p>Guidelines for new posts:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Make sure content is appropriate.</li>
      <li>Make sure the title has 5+ characters.</li>
      <li>Make sure the body has 20+ characters.</li>
      <li>Make sure that you have selected a topic.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="span8">
    <%= render partial: 'form', locals: { topic: @topic, post: @post } %>
  </div>
</div>
  